title: Jeff Farias Show - June 13, 2008 (24kbs Audio).mp3
description:
Weekdays from 3pm to 6pm

Valley resident Jeff Farias unravels the local and national news stories of the day with an upbeat, action-oriented style that has made him a listener favorite.

Jeff speaks daily with prominent authors, politicians, activists, and pundits to get behind the headlines and the hype to what really matters: what you can do about it.

Local callers and local issues make Jeff the perfect ?drive time? compliment to 1480 KPHX?s line up of national stars.
